request.description:
A JSON response is returned for a list of advanceId's. 

The purpose of this call is to retrieve any payments made for a given advanceId. This endpoint is mostly used for GUI purposes. </br> </br>
An example request will look like this:  {
 "advance": [
{
    "advanceId": 4
}, {
    "advanceId": 5
}, {
    "advanceId": 6
}, {
    "advanceId": 7
}, {
    "advanceId": 8
}, {
    "advanceId": 9
}, {
    "advanceId": 10
} ]
 }

